flowchart TB
  A[PDF or audio intake] --> B[Scan & polish the text]
  B --> C[Learn every name<br/>phonetics pass]
  C --> D[Design the episodes]
  D --> E[Enrich with context<br/>+ verify every citation]
  E --> F{Source review gate}
  F -->|pass| G[Write the narration]
  F -->|needs work| D
  G --> H[Challenger: 15 quality checks]
  H -->|fail| G
  H -->|pass| I{Publish gates}
  I -->|all 12 pass| J[Episodes + annotated chapters]
  I -->|blocked| G
